 Frosting

step 1

Beat butter until light and fluffy. 
With mixer on low speed, beat in icing sugar, cream, vanilla and salt until smooth, adding up to 2 tbsp (30 mL) more cream if needed.
 Increase speed to high; beat for 1 to 2 minutes or until frosting is light and fluffy.


 step 2

 Add frosting to piping bag fitted with round tip; pipe over cupcakes. 
 Alternatively, spoon frosting into resealable bag and clip off one corner to pipe over cupcakes, or spoon onto cupcakes.